OL,3,CCompany fined #120k after worker
OL,4,Cbreaks leg falling from roof
OL,6,FA solar energy company has been fined
OL,7,F#120,000 after one of its employees
OL,8,Ffell from a roof while working on a
OL,9,Fproperty in Salisbury.
OL,11,FThe EE Renewables Limited worker was
OL,12,Fadjusting a solar panel when he slid
OL,13,Fand fell four metres onto the ground
OL,14,Fbelow, breaking his femure.
