OL,3,CCompany fined #120k after worker
OL,4,Cbreaks leg falling from roof
OL,6,FAn investigation by the national
OL,7,Fregulator for workplace safety - the
OL,8,FHealth and Safety Executive (HSE) -
OL,9,Ffound that the company had not
OL,10,Fproperly planned the work at height
OL,11,Fand failed to take suitable steps to
OL,12,Fprevent a fall.
OL,14,FEE Renewables Limited pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto breaching Section 2(1) of the
OL,16,FHealth and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,17,F1974.
